steel_helmet, requires 30 zero tokens, description: If you wear this, it will protect you from headshots (both extra damage and fall effect) until it is broken. Its damage resistance is persistent even if taken off and re-worn after rejoining the game.=Kask, 30 zero jetonu gerektirir, kýrýlana kadar sizi kafadan vuruţlardan korur ve ayrýca yere düţmekten de korur
ladder, requires 10 zero tokens, description: Placing a Ladder creates a climbable ladder extending upwards for 20 tiles. It can also be destroyed with weapons. The player who placed the ladder can retrieve it by pressing shift + enter near its base.=Merdiven, 10 zero jetonu gerektirir, 20 birim yüksekliđe kadar týrmanabilirsiniz, ateţ edilerek yok edilebilir, üssünde dururken Shift+Enter'a basarak çantaya geri alýnabilir
barricade, requires 10 zero tokens, description: When you place a Barricade, it creates a wall structure that is 10 tiles in height, featuring a platform on top that you can stand on. It can be destroyed by weapon fire. The dirt platform on top is removed when the barricade is destroyed.=Barikat, 10 zero jetonu gerektirir, 10 birim yüksekliđindedir ve üzerinde durabilirsiniz, ateţ edilerek yok edilebilir
invisibility_shield, requires 15 zero tokens, description: When you use the Invisibility Shield, you will become invisible for 15 seconds. During this time, other players cannot see you on their nearby player list (E key) or through binoculars, and they cannot hear your beacon signal. Only your footstep sounds will be audible to others. The weapon scope feature will also not be beep for invisible players. However, opponents can still hit you with weapons if they manage to guess your location.=Sis bombasý, 15 zero jetonu gerektirir ve sizi 15 saniye boyunca gizler
