spatial_amplifier, requires 40 event points, description: If you are within 5 tiles of another player, you can press Enter (use item) to place the Spatial Amplifier on them. For the next 10 minutes, you can use the Spatial Amplifier Controller to see that player's coordinates. The amplifier can be destroyed; if it is, the affected player and any players within a 20-tile radius will hear an explosion and take damage. All players on the map will hear a distant sound of the explosion.=Takip cihazý, 40 etkinlik puaný gerektirir, düţmana 5 adým mesafeden yerleţtirebilirsiniz, 10 dakika sürer, bu sayede düţmanýn koordinatlarýný öđrenebilir veya takip cihazý kumandasýyla patlatarak düţmana ve 20 adým çevresindeki her ţeye zarar verebilirsiniz
jammer, requires 20 event points, description: When you activate a Jammer, players nearby (within its effective radius) will be unable to use Binoculars or see other players using the E key (nearby player list) for 2 minutes. Their weapon scopes will also not function during this time.=Parazit cihazý, 20 etkinlik puaný gerektirir, etkinleţtirildiđinde dürbünü bozar ve düţman E tuţunu kullanarak yerinizi öđrenemez veya iki dakika boyunca niţan alma sesini duyamaz
adrenaline_shot, requires 30 event points, description: When used, the Adrenaline Shot speeds up your weapon's fire rate for 2 minutes.=Adrenalin iđnesi, 30 etkinlik puaný gerektirir, silahýn ateţ hýzýný 2 dakika boyunca artýrýr
boom_box, requires 20 event points, description: When you use a Boom Box, it spawns a random-looking item on the ground. If any player (including yourself) tries to pick it up using shift + enter, it will explode. Nearby players, including the one who triggered it, will take damage, and you (the placer of the Boom Box) will receive 1 Zero Token.=Tuzaklý eţya, 20 etkinlik puaný gerektirir, Açýklama: Yere sahte eţyalar yerleţtirilir ve bir oyuncu Shift+Enter'a basarsa etrafýndaki her ţey patlar ve sahte eţyayý yerleţtiren kiţi bir zero jetonu kazanýr
corpse_scanner, requires 40 event points, description: Using this item will show you a list of all corpses on your current map, including their coordinates, the time remaining until they disappear, and the owner's name.=Ceset tarayýcý, 40 etkinlik puaný gerektirir, Açýklama: Bu eţya haritadaki tüm cesetleri, kaybolma sürelerini, sahiplerini ve koordinatlarýný bulmanýzý sađlar
corpse_bomb, requires 40 event points, description: This item can be toggled on or off. If it's active when you die, and another player attempts to open your corpse, the bomb will explode. Nearby players, including the one opening the corpse, will take damage. The corpse will disappear, and you will receive 1 Zero Token.=Ceset bombasý, 40 etkinlik puaný gerektirir, Açýklama: Etkinleţtirilebilir veya devre dýţý býrakýlabilir, eđer öldürülürseniz ve biri cesedinizi açmaya çalýţýrsa patlar ve onu açan da dahil olmak üzere yakýndaki oyuncularý öldürür, ceset de kaybolur ve bir zero jetonu kazanýrsýnýz
